OL,3,CThree hectares of heathland and
OL,4,Cwoodland burned in wildfire
OL,6,FFirefighters have been tackling a
OL,7,Flarge heathland and woodland fire in
OL,8,FEast Hampshire.
OL,10,FThe blaze started on Monday evening
OL,11,Foff Hammer Lane in Headley.
OL,13,FCrews from Hampshire and Surrey were
OL,14,Fbrought in as well as specialist
OL,15,Fwildfire vehicles, 4x4s and a water
OL,16,Fcarrier.
OL,18,FThey used beaters, hose reels and off
OL,19,Froad vehicles to put out the fire and
OL,20,Fremained on scene overnight to dampen
OL,21,Fhotspots.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
