OL,3,CThree hectares of heathland and
OL,4,Cwoodland burned in wildfire
OL,6,FPeople in the surrounding area were
OL,7,Fadvised to close windows and doors due
OL,8,Fto smoke.
OL,10,FAround three hectares of heathland and
OL,11,Fwoodland are believed to have been
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
